{"tid":1689772,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為 MatePad Pro 曝光   機身設計酷似 iPad Pro","createTime":"2019-11-03T03:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:47:52.000Z","uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e371d3d896e63a63790a841df7da33973600e3b","tid":1689772,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:57:08.000Z","msg":"屎為又致莖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網站 91mobiles 日前上載了一款尚未發佈的華為平板（下圖），該平板的機身設計和 Apple 的 iPad Pro 相似，但自拍鏡頭則藏在屏幕左上角的相機孔內。91mobiles 表示該華為平板將會是 MediaPad M6 的後繼型號，有可能稱呼為 MediaPad M7。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1102-1b-1059x900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F1102-1b-1059x900.jpg&h=0cb1a54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過另一著名爆料人 Evan Blass，則在 Twitter 上傳了比較清晰的產品圖片，表示平板的名字將會是 MatePad Pro。由於華為的筆電產品名叫 MateBook，所以平板產品稱為 MatePad Pro 亦不無道理。報導指這部代號 Marx 的平板，將會擁有屏幕窄邊框設計，支援華為 M-Pen 手寫筆和智能磁吸式鍵盤。<br />\n<br />\n當用戶安裝智能鍵盤後，MatePad Pro 的設計跟 iPad Pro 相當相似。根據 91mobiles 上載的圖片，平板會有黑、白兩種機身顏色，機身會有 USB-C 接口和兩組揚聲器，但未知是否提供 3.5mm 耳機輸出。"},{"pid":"3be839222fc1fc0e07bea5585b51ef612efdebc4","tid":1689772,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/11/02/huawei-matepad-pro-leak/notebook/tablet-notebook/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F11%2F02%2Fhuawei-matepad-pro-leak%2Fnotebook%2Ftablet-notebook%2F&h=e614b0cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bbe27f5cf145fe5cdc2bdf17d1c4137acd2cb2c","tid":1689772,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:02:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/11/02/huawei-matepad-pro-leak/noteb